<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Certificado de Finalizaci√≥n</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .certificate-container {
      width: 297mm;
      height: 210mm;
      border: 10px solid #004d40;
      padding: 20mm;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #e0f2f7, #ffffff);
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .header { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .header h1 { color: #004d40; font-size: 3em; margin: 0; }
    .header p { color: #555; font-size: 1.2em; }
    .content h2 { color: #00796b; font-size: 2.5em; margin-top: 30px; }
    .content p { font-size: 1.5em; color: #333; margin-top: 10px; }
    .signature { margin-top: 50px; display: flex; justify-content: space-around; }
    .signature div { border-top: 1px solid #333; padding-top: 10px; width: 40%; }
    .footer { position: absolute; bottom: 20mm; width: calc(100% - 40mm); font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; }
    .badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20mm;
      left: 20mm;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: #ffd700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      border: 3px solid #ccac00;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .linkedin-logo {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20mm;
      right: 20mm;
      width: 150px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .main-title {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #0077B5; 
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .course-title {
      font-size: 2.2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #000;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .completion-info {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .description {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
    }
    .signature-area {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
    }
    .signature-block {
      text-align: center;
      width: 45%;
    }
    .signature-line {
      border-top: 1px solid #aaa;
      padding-top: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .signer-name {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
    }
    .signer-title {
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #777;
    }
    .footer-id {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 10mm;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #999;
    }
    .side-badge {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100px;
      background-color: #f0f2f5; 
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .side-badge .circle {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: #ffd700;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      border: 3px solid #ccac00;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .side-badge .text {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #555;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transform: rotate(-90deg); 
      white-space: nowrap;
      position: absolute;
      left: -10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="certificate-container">
    <div class="side-badge">
      <div class="circle">üèÖ</div>
      <span class="text">COMPLETADO</span>
    </div>

    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/Linkedin_logo_PNG_Transparent.png/800px-Linkedin_logo_PNG_Transparent.png" alt="LinkedIn Learning Logo" class="linkedin-logo">

    <div style="margin-left: 120px; text-align: left;">
      <p style="color: #0077B5; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px;">LinkedIn Learning</p>
      <h1 class="main-title">CERTIFICADO de finalizaci√≥n</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">¬°Felicidades, {{userName}}!</p>

      <h2 class="course-title">{{courseTitle}}</h2>
      <p class="completion-info">Curso completado el {{issueDate}}</p>

      <p class="description">
        Seguir aprendiendo te ha permitido ampliar horizontes, perfeccionar tus
        aptitudes y mejorar tus posibilidades profesionales.
      </p>

      <div class="signature-area">
        <div class="signature-block">
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p class="signer-name">Dany Bednartz</p>
          <p class="signer-title">Responsable de estrategia de contenido de Learning</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signature-block">
          <div class="signature-line"></div>
          <p class="signer-name">LinkedIn Learning</p>
          <p class="signer-title">1000 W Maude Ave<br>Sunnyvale, CA 94085</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-id">ID del certificado: {{certificateId}}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
